Degree-Shift
Degree-Shift is a simple and responsive temperature converter that helps users convert temperatures 
between Celsius (°C) and Fahrenheit (°F) instantly.

Features:
✔ Celsius to Fahrenheit conversion
✔ Fahrenheit to Celsius conversion
✔ Responsive design
✔ User-friendly interface
✔ Built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript

Tech Stack:
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
